rock-bsp
===========

Getting Started
---------------

Attention : before make, you should choice the target board

1. Choose a board doing `./configure my_board`, or `./configure` to see
   the list of supported ones.

2. Run 'make' to build and pack or 'make help' to list available targets

Overview
--------

This repository provides various scripts to help hacking devices with pack-toolsSOC.

  ./scripts/
    rock_mkrootfs.sh		- Ext4 rootfs from tar.gz
    rock_mkupdateimg.sh		- Linux update image
